Teleports the caster of the rite to the location contained within a $(b)$(el:circle_magic/rites/circle_magic/binding/waystone)bound$(/el)$(/b) or $(b)$(el:circle_magic/rites/circle_magic/binding/waystone_blooded)blooded$(/el)$(/b) waystone.

The witches association has reported occasional instances of parts being left behind.
